metadata.name: Extra Executive Producer #1/5
metadata.description: Shibuya joins forces with Steve Aoki and Seth Green’s Stoopid Buddy Stoodios, the studio behind the Emmy Award-winning Robot Chicken, to present Dominion X — an interactive storytelling adventure that puts you smack dab in the middle of the creation of an animated series. This NFT represents each user's participation in the creation of the animated series and engagement to make this show possible.
